The NEWS file for the HpiInfo package.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v3.0.2 - 19 February 2025

Changes:
   Bugfix. Fixed a bug in hpiinfo-cmd(1) that caused adapters to be
   misidentified when using non-contiguous index values.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v3.0.1 - 19 February 2025

Changes:
   Bugfix. Added missing dependency info to the DEB package.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v3.0.0 - 17 February 2025

Changes:
   Command-line Utility. Added a hpiinfo-cmd(1) utility to allow basic
   adapter information to be accessed from user scripts.

   Qt Toolkit. Updated the required major Qt version from Qt5 to Qt6.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v2.0.1 - 13 April 2023

Changes:
   Enabled 'usermode' priviledge escalation to allow starting from menu
   on Debian-ish distros.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v2.0.0 - 17 June 2021

Changes:
   Updated to use Qt5.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v1.0.2 - 20 March 2018

Changes:
   Fixed a bug that caused launch from a menu item to fail.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v1.0.1 - 20 March 2018

First production release.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
